"title": "5178: running",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5178: running",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture gives pictures of running in both its literal and metaphorical senses, the image of the Christian life as a race being particularly significant.</p>\n<h2>Running away</h2>\n<h3>Fleeing in battle</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:27\">EXO 23:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:36-Lev26:37\">LEV 26:36–26:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:12\">JOS 7:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh8:3-Josh8:19\">JOS 8:3–8:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam14:20-1Sam14:22\">1SA 14:20–14:22</a></p>\n<h3>Escaping from danger</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov18:10\">PRO 18:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:12-Gen19:22\">GEN 19:12–19:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh6:10-Neh6:11\">NEH 6:10–6:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa10:1-Isa10:3\">ISA 10:1–10:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:16\">JER 17:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer48:4-Jer48:6\">JER 48:4–48:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:6\">JER 51:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:44-Jer51:45\">JER 51:44–51:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos2:14-Amos2:16\">AMO 2:14–2:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:12-John10:13\">JHN 10:12–10:13</a></p>\n<h3>Running away from individuals</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam19:11-1Sam19:12\">1SA 19:11–19:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen16:6-Gen16:8\">GEN 16:6–16:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:20-Gen31:21\">GEN 31:20–31:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen39:11-Gen39:15\">GEN 39:11–39:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:2-John10:5\">JHN 10:2–10:5</a></p>\n<h3>Running away from God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah1:1-Jonah1:10\">JON 1:1–1:10</a></p>\n<h3>Running away from evil</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:22\">2TI 2:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:18\">1CO 6:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:14\">1CO 10:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:11\">1TI 6:11</a></p>\n<h2>Running after people or things</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps16:4\">PSA 16:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth3:10\">RUT 3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:11\">ISA 5:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:23-Jer2:25\">JER 2:23–2:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:32-Ezek16:34\">EZK 16:32–16:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:28-Matt6:34\">MAT 6:28–6:34</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:27-Luke12:31\">LUK 12:27–12:31</a></p>\n<h2>Running in eagerness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:1-John20:4\">JHN 20:1–20:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr23:12\">2CH 23:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:25\">MRK 9:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:22-Luke17:23\">LUK 17:22–17:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:11\">ACT 3:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:30\">ACT 21:30</a></p>\n<h2>Running swiftly</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job9:25\">JOB 9:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job39:13-Job39:18\">JOB 39:13–39:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl9:11\">ECC 9:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer12:5\">JER 12:5</a></p>\n<h2>Heralds running ahead of a dignitary</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam8:11\">1SA 8:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam15:1\">2SA 15:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs1:5\">1KI 1:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:46\">1KI 18:46</a></p>\n<h2>Messages carried by runners</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam18:19\">2SA 18:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam18:21-2Sam18:32\">2SA 18:21–18:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:25-2Kgs4:31\">2KI 4:25–4:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs5:20-2Kgs5:23\">2KI 5:20–5:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs9:1-2Kgs9:3\">2KI 9:1–9:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:15\">PSA 147:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:21\">JER 23:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:2\">HAB 2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech2:3-Zech2:5\">ZEC 2:3–2:5</a></p>\n<h2>The life of the believer likened to running a race</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:2\">GAL 2:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:32\">PSA 119:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov4:10-Prov4:12\">PRO 4:10–4:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:30-Isa40:31\">ISA 40:30–40:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:24\">ACT 20:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:24-1Cor9:27\">1CO 9:24–9:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:7\">GAL 5:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:14-Phil2:16\">PHP 2:14–2:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:6-2Tim4:8\">2TI 4:6–4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:1\">HEB 12:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:9\">2JN 1:9</a></p>",
